# Per-Dockerfile ignore for the Kokoro TTS image. Unlike the repo-root
# .dockerignore (which drops the model weights to keep the backend/frontend
# contexts small), this one KEEPS kokoro/ since the TTS image needs the
# weights + voice packs. Everything else heavy/irrelevant is still excluded.
.git
.venv
venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/node_modules
*.wav
legacy
reader_app/deploy
reader_app/docker
podcast_transcript.json
bib_text.txt
spoken_text.txt
*.bak
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.claude
# kokoro/ is deliberately NOT excluded here.
